response.overview: Yıldız returns to her childhood home to face the memories she tried to bury. Moments of warmth clash with dark, twisted recollections as she plays the piano that once brought her comfort. But as the music unfolds, so do the secrets. The house remembers everything, and some melodies were never meant to be heard again.
response.tagline: Some songs aren’t meant to be heard.
response.title: Keys of the Past
